[7] FAIL2BAN	# specofy ip in logfile so they want login

INSTALLATION
$ sudo apt install fail2ban -y

PRIMARY CONFIGURATION FILE / JAIL FILE
/etc/fail2ban/jail.conf

WE CAN INCLUDE A BLACKLIST AND WHITE LIST TO PERFORM CERTAIN OPERATION
